What is Balayage?
Balayage is a freehand hair coloring technique that creates a natural, graduated effect. Unlike traditional highlights, balayage involves painting the color directly onto the hair, resulting in a softer, more blended look. This technique is perfect for those looking to achieve a low-maintenance yet sophisticated style. At Code Hair, we specialize in balayage, making us the best balayage in Dubai for women seeking this trendy and versatile look.

